Who's News:
   Capital Cities Names
   Cain to Network Post
Also, Marvin F. Goldsmith, 50, was named to the new
position of president of sales and marketing for the ABC
network. He will take on the responsibilities of H. Weller
(Jake) Keever, executive vice president of sales, who is
retiring. Mr. Goldsmith had been general sales manager, with
a responsibility for prime time sales.
   The appointments of Messrs. Cain and Goldsmith are
effective Feb. 3.